sql.query:
SELECT s.uuid AS student_uuid, s.firstName, s.lastName, SUM(ce.enrolgrandtotal) AS student_total, COUNT(ce.enrolment_uuid) AS enrol_count
FROM students AS s
LEFT JOIN charges_enrolments AS ce ON (ce.student_uuid = s.uuid)
WHERE ce.charge_uuid = :P1 /* {{$_GET.charge_uuid}} */
GROUP BY s.uuid, s.firstName, s.lastName

SELECT *
FROM payments_familycharges AS pf
WHERE uuid IN ({{family_charge.payments.unstringify() || []}})

SELECT DISTINCT e.uuid, c.startTimeDisplay, c.day AS classday, c.instructor_uuid, c.classlevel_uuid, e.startDate, e.dropDate
FROM enrolments AS e
INNER JOIN charges_enrolments AS ce ON (ce.enrolment_uuid = e.uuid) INNER JOIN classes AS c ON (c.uuid = e.class_uuid)
WHERE ce.charge_uuid = :P1 /* {{$_GET.charge_uuid}} */ AND e.student_uuid = :P2 /* {{student_uuid}} */

SELECT DISTINCT cl.startTimeDecimal, cl.day AS classday, cl.instructor_uuid, cl.classlevel_uuid, enrolments.startDate, enrolments.dropDate, SUM(pec.amount) AS total_paid, ce.uuid, ce.id, ce.startofweek, ce.class_uuid, ce.student_uuid, ce.classtype_uuid, ce.enrolment_uuid, ce.classDate, ce.baseRate, ce.endisc, ce.ennetrate, ce.endiscdescription, ce.endiscdescription, ce.endiscrate, ce.familydiscountdesc, ce.familydiscountrate, ce.familydiscounttotal, ce.enrolsubtotal, ce.holding_fee, ce.holding_fee_discount, ce.enrolgrandtotal, ce.charge_uuid, ce.created, ce.updated, ce.created_by, ce.updated_by
FROM charges_enrolments AS ce
LEFT JOIN classes AS cl ON (cl.uuid = ce.class_uuid) LEFT JOIN enrolments ON (enrolments.uuid = ce.enrolment_uuid) LEFT JOIN payments_enrolcharges AS pec ON (pec.enrolcharge_uuid = ce.uuid)
WHERE ce.charge_uuid = :P1 /* {{$_GET.charge_uuid}} */ AND ce.enrolment_uuid = :P2 /* {{uuid}} */
GROUP BY cl.startTimeDecimal, cl.day, cl.instructor_uuid, cl.classlevel_uuid, enrolments.startDate, enrolments.dropDate, ce.uuid, ce.id, ce.startofweek, ce.class_uuid, ce.student_uuid, ce.classtype_uuid, ce.enrolment_uuid, ce.classDate, ce.baseRate, ce.endisc, ce.ennetrate, ce.endiscdescription, ce.endiscdescription, ce.endiscrate, ce.familydiscountdesc, ce.familydiscountrate, ce.familydiscounttotal, ce.enrolsubtotal, ce.holding_fee, ce.holding_fee_discount, ce.enrolgrandtotal, ce.charge_uuid, ce.created, ce.updated, ce.created_by, ce.updated_by
ORDER BY ce.startofweek ASC, ce.classDate ASC, cl.startTimeDecimal ASC

SELECT DISTINCT ce.startofweek, cl.uuid AS class_uuid, cl.instructor_uuid, cl.classlevel_uuid, cl.day AS classday, cl.startTimeDecimal, cl.startTimeDisplay, cl.endTimeDisplay, enrolments.dropDate, enrolments.student_uuid, enrolments.startDate, ce.classDate, ce.baseRate, ce.endisc, ce.ennetrate, ce.endiscdescription, ce.endiscrate, ce.familydiscountdesc, ce.familydiscountrate, ce.familydiscounttotal, ce.enrolsubtotal, ce.holding_fee, ce.holding_fee_discount, ce.enrolgrandtotal, ce.charge_uuid, ce.created, ce.updated, ce.created_by, ce.updated_by
FROM charges_enrolments AS ce
LEFT JOIN classes AS cl ON (cl.uuid = ce.class_uuid) INNER JOIN enrolments ON (enrolments.uuid = ce.enrolment_uuid) INNER JOIN payments_enrolcharges AS pec ON (pec.enrolcharge_uuid = ce.uuid)
WHERE ce.charge_uuid = :P1 /* {{$_GET.charge_uuid}} */ AND ce.enrolment_uuid = :P2 /* {{uuid}} */
ORDER BY ce.startofweek ASC, ce.classDate ASC, cl.startTimeDecimal ASC
